    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> until you end up with a pile of cheese shavings</p><p>Combine your <strong>pesto</strong> and <strong>mayo </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>pesto mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
