        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> in <strong>cling film</strong> and bash with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until flattened to approx. 1cm thickness</p><p>Add a handful of <strong>flour </strong>to a plate, a splash of <strong>milk </strong>to a shallow bowl and your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a separate plate</p><p>Season the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, coat in <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add to the <strong>milk </strong>and firmly press into the <strong>breadcrumbs </strong>to evenly coat all over</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1675769551302-x200.jpg",
